{"id":11848,"date":"2013-01-29T01:32:08","date_gmt":"2013-01-29T06:32:08","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=11848"},"modified":"2025-06-24T22:24:45","modified_gmt":"2025-06-24T18:24:45","slug":"faith-merciful-creation","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/29\/faith-merciful-creation\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Mercy: None has faith until merciful to creation"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Musa al-Ashari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<b>You will never have faith until you love each other. Shall I tell you what will make you love each other<\/b>?\u201d They said, \u201cOf course, O Messenger of Allah.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Spread peace between yourselves. By the One in whose hand is my soul, you will not enter Paradise until you are merciful to others<\/b>.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, all of us are merciful.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<b>Verily, it is not only\u00a0mercy between yourselves, but rather it is mercy for everyone.<\/b>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: al-Sunan al-Kubra\u0304 lil-Nasa\u0304&#8217;i\u0304 5760<\/p>\n<p>Grade:\u00a0<b><i>Sahih <\/i><\/b>(authentic) according to Al-Mundhiri<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0623\u064e\u0634\u0652\u0639\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0644\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0624\u0652\u0645\u0650\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u062d\u064e\u062a\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u062a\u064e\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0628\u064f\u0648\u0627 \u0623\u064