ove each other? Spread peace\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Featured&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Featured","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/featured\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42697,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/ninety-nine-rahma-awliya\/","url_meta":{"origin":11848,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Awliya: Ninety-nine mercies reserved for Allah\u2019s allies","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Haydah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty created one hundred portions of mercy, so one portion of mercy between His creation is that they are merciful to each other by it, and ninety-nine portions are reserved for His allies.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42693,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/allah-merciful-animals\/","url_meta":{"origin":11848,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah rewards compassion to animals","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Ma\u2019qil ibn Yasar reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, I had taken the goat to slaughter it, but I had mercy on it.\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIf you had mercy on it, Allah will have mercy on you.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 10557\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.co